Class PlacesApi

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.PlacesApi

  • public class PlacesApi
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract representation of Place API endpoint. Provides executors that can be used to handle all place-related requests.
